c graph-matching-v0 triangle-no-perfect-matching
c Variables select edges of K3: 1=(a,b), 2=(b,c), 3=(a,c).
c The first three clauses require every vertex to be covered by a selected edge.
c The last three clauses require every vertex to be covered by at most one edge.
p cnf 3 6
1 3 0
1 2 0
2 3 0
-1 -3 0
-1 -2 0
-2 -3 0
